but cars are driving in
one after another today.

00:25:24.586 --> 00:25:26.046
WIFE

00:25:28.131 --> 00:25:30.175
The person you called is unavailable.

00:25:49.194 --> 00:25:50.028
Ji-yu!

00:25:51.488 --> 00:25:52.530
Ji-yu!

00:25:55.075 --> 00:25:56.076
Are you okay?

00:25:57.869 --> 00:25:59.454
Are you hurt anywhere?

00:25:59.537 --> 00:26:01.081
Mom, I'm sorry.

00:26:01.164 --> 00:26:04.042
Why would you be sorry? I'm sorry.

00:26:04.125 --> 00:26:05.293
Are you hurt anywhere?

00:26:05.377 --> 00:26:06.336
No.

00:26:10.924 --> 00:26:13.385
Goodness.

00:26:13.468 --> 00:26:15.512
This is my favorite scene.

00:26:17.972 --> 00:26:19.766
I almost missed it.

00:26:21.768 --> 00:26:22.936
What do you want?

00:26:38.201 --> 00:26:39.119
Goal.

00:26:41.621 --> 00:26:42.831
Let Ji-yu go.

00:26:43.456 --> 00:26:44.582
Then I'll keep

00:26:44.666 --> 00:26:46.668
my mouth shut forever as you wish.

00:26:48.086 --> 00:26:49.379
You're the evidence.

00:26:50.588 --> 00:26:51.840
I should get rid of it.

00:26:52.382 --> 00:26:54.759
I can't live worrying about it forever.

00:26:55.593 --> 00:26:58.555
The historic moment from 15 years ago

00:26:58.638 --> 00:27:01.349
that dominated the news

00:27:01.933 --> 00:27:03.893
will hit the headlines again.

00:27:05.103 --> 00:27:06.771
I'll do whatever you say.

00:27:07.272 --> 00:27:08.523
Just spare Ji-yu.

00:27:09.274 --> 00:27:10.233
Let, let Ji-yu go.

00:27:10.316 --> 00:27:11.234
Mom!

00:27:11.317 --> 00:27:13.111
This has nothing to do with her!

00:27:14.362 --> 00:27:16.448
It had nothing to do with the old woman

00:27:16.531 --> 00:27:17.740
who got in the accident.

00:27:23.246 --> 00:27:24.122
Please, I beg you.

00:27:24.205 --> 00:27:26.708
Yang Hoon, please just spare Ji-yu.

00:27:26.791 --> 00:27:28.209
Let her go!

00:27:29.794 --> 00:27:30.962
Darn it.

00:27:33.256 --> 00:27:34.299
Are you serious?

00:27:35.884 --> 00:27:38.678
I respected you so much,
and you're begging me

00:27:39.554 --> 00:27:41.389
just to spare your kid?

00:27:43.433 --> 00:27:45.143
Just spare Ji-yu, Yang Hoon.

00:27:45.226 --> 00:27:47.687
I beg you. Spare her, Yang Hoon!

00:27:49.147 --> 00:27:51.316
Are you going to burn the place down?

00:27:51.399 --> 00:27:53.067
Do you think you can get away with this?

00:27:53.693 --> 00:27:54.944
Fire?

00:27:55.028 --> 00:27:56.279
That won't work.

00:27:56.362 --> 00:27:58.573
Firefighters arrive very quickly nowadays.

00:28:01.618 --> 00:28:04.996
Everyone thinks fire itself kills people,

00:28:05.079 --> 00:28:07.081
but the one that's really dangerous

00:28:07.165 --> 00:28:08.541
is toxic gas.

00:28:11.002 --> 00:28:12.545
I'm the CEO

00:28:12.629 --> 00:28:14.380
of a chemical plant, you see.

00:28:17.217 --> 00:28:18.176
This is

00:28:18.801 --> 00:28:20.470
phosgene.

00:28:20.553 --> 00:28:23.431
And it's very dangerous.

00:28:23.515 --> 00:28:25.225
No.

00:28:25.934 --> 00:28:27.894
Mr. Jung, finish this.

00:28:28.561 --> 00:28:30.271
-Yes, sir.
-Yang Hoon!

00:28:30.355 --> 00:28:31.439
Yang Hoon!

00:28:48.623 --> 00:28:51.543
They say fire is the best sight to watch.

00:28:53.461 --> 00:28:54.295
It's nothing much.

00:28:55.839 --> 00:28:56.881
Yang Hoon.

00:28:56.965 --> 00:28:59.050
Gosh, you startled me.

00:28:59.926 --> 00:29:00.969
I'm sorry.

00:29:01.052 --> 00:29:03.680
Repent all you want in there.

00:29:04.514 --> 00:29:05.849
Have fun with your daughter.

00:29:06.516 --> 00:29:10.478
At least the mom and the daughter
will be together until the end.

00:29:11.521 --> 00:29:12.939
That makes me feel relieved.

00:29:13.648 --> 00:29:14.816
Just let Ji-yu go.

00:29:17.026 --> 00:29:18.236
Please let her go!

00:29:18.319 --> 00:29:19.153
Yang Hoon!

00:29:19.612 --> 00:29:21.072
Yang Hoon, open the door!

00:29:21.155 --> 00:29:22.407
Open the door!

00:29:23.449 --> 00:29:24.742
Let Ji-yu go!

00:29:24.826 --> 00:29:27.370
Yang Hoon, let Ji-yu go!

00:29:49.517 --> 00:29:51.352
Mom, I'm sorry. It's my fault.

00:29:51.436 --> 00:29:54.480
Shush, don't say anything.
You can't breathe in the gas.

00:29:58.735 --> 00:30:00.069
There's someone here!

00:30:42.946 --> 00:30:44.322
Save me.

00:30:46.699 --> 00:30:48.076
Mom.

00:30:48.159 --> 00:30:50.161
-Did you hear that too?
-Yes.

00:30:50.244 --> 00:30:51.829
There's someone here.

00:30:54.916 --> 00:30:56.250
Save me.

00:31:13.893 --> 00:31:14.852
Honey!

00:31:23.194 --> 00:31:24.153
Ji-yu.

00:31:24.904 --> 00:31:26.280
Ji-yu!

00:31:28.825 --> 00:31:30.118
Ji-yu.

00:31:43.339 --> 00:31:44.424
Ji-yu.

00:31:45.008 --> 00:31:46.926
Ji-yu. Hyun Ji-yu.

00:31:56.519 --> 00:31:57.478
Ji-yu.

00:31:59.188 --> 00:32:00.148
Ji-yu.

00:32:00.898 --> 00:32:01.816
Ji-yu. Hyun Ji-yu.

00:32:04.360 --> 00:32:05.194
Dad.

00:32:06.612 --> 00:32:07.822
Dad is here.

00:32:07.905 --> 00:32:09.198
I'm here, so don't worry.

00:32:09.782 --> 00:32:11.200
You'll be fine soon.

00:32:11.617 --> 00:32:12.493
Where's Mom?

00:32:16.539 --> 00:32:17.999
Mom…

00:32:18.082 --> 00:32:19.208
Can you go alone?

00:32:19.292 --> 00:32:20.668
No, don't go.

00:32:20.752 --> 00:32:22.545
I'll take her and get out soon.

00:32:22.628 --> 00:32:24.672
It's dangerous here. Wait outside.

00:32:25.214 --> 00:32:28.176
You'll go back in there
when you don't even know who she is?

00:32:28.885 --> 00:32:30.011
You can't.

00:32:31.971 --> 00:32:34.057
What would Dad have done?

00:32:36.976 --> 00:32:38.352
If Dad were here,

00:32:38.436 --> 00:32:40.354
he'd never give up on saving someone.

00:32:41.856 --> 00:32:42.774
Mom.

00:32:47.153 --> 00:32:48.279
I'll be back soon.

00:32:50.073 --> 00:32:51.032
Mom.

00:32:52.033 --> 00:32:54.410
She was with me until just now.

00:32:56.829 --> 00:32:59.165
She went back in to save someone.

00:33:01.584 --> 00:33:03.836
I'll go get her. Wait here.

00:33:41.124 --> 00:33:42.250
Lee Hwa-jin?

00:33:42.792 --> 00:33:43.876
What should I do?

00:33:43.960 --> 00:33:47.171
If there's a victim,
there should be a perpetrator.

00:33:47.255 --> 00:33:50.675
She killed Cha Su-yeon and her daughter
to avenge her mom

00:33:50.758 --> 00:33:52.218
and died herself too.

00:33:52.301 --> 00:33:53.469
It's neat.

00:33:53.553 --> 00:33:54.470
Yes, sir.

00:33:55.012 --> 00:33:55.847
Text a will

00:33:56.139 --> 00:33:58.474
to her friend
and get rid of them all here.

00:34:00.601 --> 00:34:02.687
Lee Hwa-jin!

00:34:08.484 --> 00:34:09.610
Ms. Cha.

00:34:33.926 --> 00:34:35.428
Don't worry.

00:34:35.511 --> 00:34:36.679
We can go out.

00:34:54.822 --> 00:34:55.823
Lee Hwa-jin.

00:34:56.324 --> 00:34:57.283
Hwa-jin!

00:35:05.124 --> 00:35:06.334
I'll do it.

00:35:06.417 --> 00:35:07.418
Honey.

00:35:07.501 --> 00:35:09.420
Stand back. I'll open it quickly.

00:35:37.323 --> 00:35:38.908
Are you okay? Are you hurt?

00:35:38.991 --> 00:35:39.992
I'm fine.

00:35:40.701 --> 00:35:41.744
What about Ji-yu?

00:35:41.827 --> 00:35:42.954
Ji-yu is fine too.

00:35:43.496 --> 00:35:44.372
Let's go.

00:35:44.872 --> 00:35:45.790
Wait.

00:35:46.332 --> 00:35:47.291
Hwa-jin.

00:35:47.375 --> 00:35:48.542
Hwa-jin?

00:35:48.626 --> 00:35:51.462
She passed out.

00:35:52.588 --> 00:35:53.506
Here.

00:35:54.340 --> 00:35:55.675
-Hwa-jin.
-Hwa-jin.

00:35:55.758 --> 00:35:57.134
-Lee Hwa-jin.
-Lee Hwa-jin.

00:35:58.511 --> 00:35:59.470
Hwa-jin.

00:36:11.232 --> 00:36:12.358
Watch out!

00:36:59.196 --> 00:37:00.197
Lee Hwa-jin.

00:37:01.073 --> 00:37:01.991
Hwa-jin.

00:37:02.783 --> 00:37:03.784
Hwa-jin.

00:37:08.789 --> 00:37:09.832
Can you hear me?

00:37:31.228 --> 00:37:32.146
Honey.

00:37:37.777 --> 00:37:38.736
Honey.

00:37:39.362 --> 00:37:40.738
Give me a second.

00:37:40.821 --> 00:37:42.323
I'll get you out soon.

00:38:05.721 --> 00:38:06.680
Honey.

00:38:09.725 --> 00:38:12.353
I'm sorry. Because of me, Yang Hoon…

00:38:15.731 --> 00:38:16.899
Don't be sorry.

00:38:19.026 --> 00:38:20.736
I should've known

00:38:22.405 --> 00:38:24.198
why you did that.

00:38:24.990 --> 00:38:26.575
I should've known.

00:38:27.576 --> 00:38:28.869
I'm sorry.

00:38:30.454 --> 00:38:31.497
No.

00:38:32.373 --> 00:38:35.167
You did nothing wrong. Don't say that.

00:38:35.251 --> 00:38:37.002
Do you still not get it?

00:38:38.879 --> 00:38:40.423
My biggest fault

00:38:41.048 --> 00:38:42.800
is that I didn't know.

00:38:44.552 --> 00:38:46.887
I of all people should've known

00:38:48.180 --> 00:38:50.891
what you did and why you did it.

00:38:51.559 --> 00:38:55.020
What my loved one did and why.

00:38:56.480 --> 00:38:57.857
I should've known.

00:39:02.862 --> 00:39:03.821
Honey.

00:39:18.878 --> 00:39:19.795
Honey.

00:39:22.923 --> 00:39:24.592
The building is cracking.

00:39:25.468 --> 00:39:27.678
It could collapse at any time. So…

00:39:31.599 --> 00:39:32.933
take Hwa-jin and leave.

00:39:41.317 --> 00:39:42.485
No.

00:39:43.527 --> 00:39:44.528
I won't.

00:39:48.324 --> 00:39:49.533
Take the girl and leave.

00:39:49.617 --> 00:39:50.576
I don't want to.

00:39:51.243 --> 00:39:52.411
Now. There's no time.

00:39:52.495 --> 00:39:53.662
No!

00:39:53.746 --> 00:39:55.498
No!

00:39:55.998 --> 00:39:56.957
No!

00:39:57.875 --> 00:39:59.710
-I won't!
-There's no time. Go now!

00:39:59.793 --> 00:40:01.545
No, I won't!

00:40:01.629 --> 00:40:04.423
Just wait. I can do this!

00:40:06.050 --> 00:40:07.051
-Honey.
-No.

00:40:08.135 --> 00:40:09.220
Think about Ji-yu.

00:40:09.303 --> 00:40:11.138
No, honey. Don't do this.

00:40:11.222 --> 00:40:12.515
No.

00:40:12.598 --> 00:40:13.933
Don't do this.

00:40:14.016 --> 00:40:15.601
Go out with her. Don't give up.

00:40:15.684 --> 00:40:17.144
I can't leave without you.

00:40:17.228 --> 00:40:20.272
No, don't do this.
Please don't do this to me.

00:40:20.856 --> 00:40:22.191
-No.
-I'll leave it to you.

00:40:23.192 --> 00:40:24.777
-No.
-Go now!

00:40:35.120 --> 00:40:37.581
Ji-yu is waiting. Get out now.

00:40:54.348 --> 00:40:56.559
Honey, hang in there. I'll be back soon.

00:40:56.642 --> 00:40:58.602
Just hang in there for a bit.

00:40:58.686 --> 00:41:00.563
Okay? I'll be back soon.

00:41:02.815 --> 00:41:04.733
Get up. Let's go.

00:41:04.817 --> 00:41:06.318
Stand up.

00:41:06.402 --> 00:41:08.320
-Dad.
-Stand up now.

00:41:16.829 --> 00:41:17.871
Dad.

00:41:20.291 --> 00:41:21.584
Dad.

00:41:38.017 --> 00:41:39.226
You have a photo, right?

00:41:59.079 --> 00:42:00.122
Goodness.

00:42:00.706 --> 00:42:04.335
Your daughter looks just like your wife.

00:42:07.713 --> 00:42:09.506
Don't be too disappointed, though.

00:42:09.590 --> 00:42:12.384
Now that I take a closer look,
she has your eyes.

00:42:32.988 --> 00:42:34.448
You worked hard.

00:42:50.923 --> 00:42:52.800
Do you know how rough it was?

00:42:57.388 --> 00:42:59.264
I really had a hard time.

00:43:03.352 --> 00:43:04.520
I know.

00:43:05.938 --> 00:43:06.772
I really--

00:43:06.855 --> 00:43:08.065
You did…

00:43:10.567 --> 00:43:12.111
a great job.

00:43:34.925 --> 00:43:36.093
I'm sorry.

00:45:33.043 --> 00:45:34.044
You're awake.

00:45:35.712 --> 00:45:37.130
Why're you sleeping like this?

00:45:39.132 --> 00:45:40.425
I came home late.

00:45:41.677 --> 00:45:43.554
I was going to rest for five minutes.

00:45:44.846 --> 00:45:47.182
But I was too tired and fell asleep.

00:45:47.266 --> 00:45:49.017
You must be very tired.

00:45:49.101 --> 00:45:51.061
Sleep comfortably on the bed.

00:45:53.355 --> 00:45:54.356
Just five minutes.

00:45:55.107 --> 00:45:56.650
Let's stay like this for five.

00:45:57.401 --> 00:45:59.736
You have an appointment at dawn.

00:45:59.820 --> 00:46:00.779
Get up now.

00:46:00.862 --> 00:46:02.030
Then one minute.

00:46:37.399 --> 00:46:38.358
What is it?

00:46:41.653 --> 00:46:43.155
Why look at me that way?

00:46:44.489 --> 00:46:45.949
Is something on my face?

00:46:48.785 --> 00:46:49.828
Honey.

00:46:58.587 --> 00:47:00.339
Are you really here?

00:47:05.302 --> 00:47:07.596
It's the shortest minute in the world.

00:48:13.412 --> 00:48:14.705
Ms. Cha?

00:48:23.296 --> 00:48:24.756
Where's my husband?

00:49:00.417 --> 00:49:04.212
Yang was arrested warrantless
for setting the old factory on fire.

00:49:04.296 --> 00:49:06.423
I don't know anything. It wasn't me!

00:49:06.506 --> 00:49:08.049
Yang denied his charge,

00:49:08.633 --> 00:49:11.762
but Jung and Kim who were arrested
for setting the fire

00:49:11.845 --> 00:49:14.931
as per Yang's orders admitted their crime.

00:49:16.057 --> 00:49:18.477
They kidnapped President-elect's daughter,

00:49:18.560 --> 00:49:20.437
lured Ms. Cha to the factory,

00:49:20.520 --> 00:49:22.939
and tried to kill them
by starting the fire.

00:49:24.608 --> 00:49:25.650
The police secured

00:49:25.734 --> 00:49:29.029
evidence that Yang was involved in
the car accident a few days ago

00:49:29.112 --> 00:49:30.572
and are interrogating him.

00:49:36.495 --> 00:49:39.247
Ms. Cha and her daughter
were rescued safely,

00:49:39.331 --> 00:49:42.167
but President-elect,
who saved his family from the fire,

00:49:42.250 --> 00:49:43.835
went missing.

00:49:44.503 --> 00:49:47.631
The search authorities are
continuing the search for two days,

00:49:47.714 --> 00:49:50.801
but some are expressing their concerns

00:49:50.884 --> 00:49:52.761
that the golden hour has already passed.

00:49:54.471 --> 00:49:56.056
-Dad.
-Stand up now.

00:49:56.640 --> 00:49:57.808
Dad.

00:50:14.032 --> 00:50:15.158
Ms. Sung

00:50:16.952 --> 00:50:19.538
wanted to talk to you about your mom.

00:50:22.916 --> 00:50:25.126
About my mom?

00:50:28.046 --> 00:50:29.089
I'm sorry.

00:50:30.006 --> 00:50:30.841
What?

00:50:32.342 --> 00:50:34.052
Why're you suddenly apologizing?

00:50:35.387 --> 00:50:37.514
On the day of the accident,

00:50:37.597 --> 00:50:38.807
I chased

00:50:40.308 --> 00:50:41.726
after your mom.

00:50:44.604 --> 00:50:46.189
You chased after my mom?

00:50:47.566 --> 00:50:49.025
To see her daughter…

00:50:51.361 --> 00:50:53.947
To see her daughter even from a distance,

00:50:55.991 --> 00:50:59.286
she came by for the whole week,
and I spotted her.

00:51:01.496 --> 00:51:02.455
But

00:51:03.415 --> 00:51:06.209
she ran away when I recognized her.

00:52:08.396 --> 00:52:10.690
Mom came

00:52:10.774 --> 00:52:12.525
to see me?

00:52:14.235 --> 00:52:15.362
I'm sure of it.

00:52:16.905 --> 00:52:18.323
This old woman here

00:52:18.949 --> 00:52:21.159
got too scared.

00:52:24.371 --> 00:52:25.830
I ended up running away.

00:52:27.248 --> 00:52:28.083
I'm sorry.

00:52:30.085 --> 00:52:31.169
I'm sorry.

00:52:34.255 --> 00:52:35.382
I'm sorry.

00:52:45.016 --> 00:52:49.896
TESTIMONY BY SHIN HAE-RIN

00:53:11.751 --> 00:53:13.128
What about President-elect?

00:53:17.507 --> 00:53:18.591
He's still missing?

00:53:26.766 --> 00:53:30.061
The unprecedented situation
of President-elect being missing

00:53:30.145 --> 00:53:32.772
made the politicians dumbfounded.

00:53:33.356 --> 00:53:35.859
Both the Participation People's party

00:53:35.942 --> 00:53:38.903
and Party for Peace and Freedom
are wishing for his safe return.

00:53:38.987 --> 00:53:42.615
The Presidential Transition Committee
hasn't announced their stance,

00:53:42.699 --> 00:53:45.744
except that they're sticking to
their transitioning duties.

00:53:57.464 --> 00:53:58.339
Hello?

00:53:58.423 --> 00:53:59.340
How's the Committee?

00:54:00.633 --> 00:54:01.468
Secretary Shin.

00:54:02.052 --> 00:54:04.220
I heard Ms. Cha was attending it.

00:54:04.721 --> 00:54:05.555
Yes.

00:54:06.473 --> 00:54:08.141
She'll attend on the day

00:54:08.224 --> 00:54:09.434
Mr. Hyun was supposed to.

00:54:10.226 --> 00:54:12.395
She has something to say about the fire.

00:54:14.856 --> 00:54:16.066
Minister nominations?

00:54:20.445 --> 00:54:22.447
The inauguration is around the corner.

00:54:22.530 --> 00:54:24.407
President-elect has high standards.

00:54:24.491 --> 00:54:25.784
You must check thoroughly.

00:54:27.243 --> 00:54:28.453
Don't worry.

00:54:29.704 --> 00:54:32.582
I'm handling all the tasks
you used to work on.

00:54:33.625 --> 00:54:37.754
President-elect
doesn't accept sloppy work.

00:54:37.837 --> 00:54:39.714
I'm working like there's no weekends.

00:54:40.715 --> 00:54:42.634
I'm losing so much weight.

00:54:46.638 --> 00:54:49.099
I thought you could wear one of these
to go to the Committee.

00:54:50.266 --> 00:54:53.311
Since the occasion is such…

00:54:57.857 --> 00:54:59.150
He…

00:55:00.902 --> 00:55:02.237
is alive.

00:55:05.115 --> 00:55:05.949
I apologize.

00:55:12.163 --> 00:55:14.541
Ms. Cha attended
the Special Committee meeting

00:55:14.624 --> 00:55:17.252
this afternoon in President-elect's stead.

00:55:17.335 --> 00:55:19.754
Ms. Cha was accused of being involved

00:55:19.838 --> 00:55:22.507
with Chairman Yang Hoon of H Chemical.

00:55:22.590 --> 00:55:25.176
People are wondering
if she'll reveal the truth.

