The contract workers

00:55:27.971 --> 00:55:30.431
and the police who forced their way

00:55:31.099 --> 00:55:32.725
into the factory to drag out

00:55:33.768 --> 00:55:37.063
the sit-in protesters
caused the fire 15 years ago.

00:55:37.981 --> 00:55:41.985
Do Tae-hun and other union members
were innocent victims.

00:55:42.068 --> 00:55:43.653
So are the six people

00:55:43.736 --> 00:55:47.115
who were at the scene of the fire,
including Song In-gyeong

00:55:47.198 --> 00:55:48.616
and Kang In-gyu.

