If what you're saying is true,

00:56:02.797 --> 00:56:04.132
you yourself

00:56:04.799 --> 00:56:06.926
won't be free from the responsibility.

00:56:08.887 --> 00:56:12.682
I already made the same statement
to the police.

00:56:13.808 --> 00:56:15.602
I won't hide

00:56:15.685 --> 00:56:17.103
or run anymore.

00:56:18.479 --> 00:56:20.231
I'll take responsibility.

00:56:20.315 --> 00:56:22.525
I'll accept the punishment too.

00:56:22.609 --> 00:56:23.943
But

00:56:24.027 --> 00:56:27.071
Yang Hoon and the contractors
aren't the only criminals.

00:56:27.155 --> 00:56:29.490
Late Cha Jin-taek
of Party for Peace and Freedom

00:56:29.574 --> 00:56:32.452
framed innocent Do Tae-hun
to be the perpetrator.

00:56:34.078 --> 00:56:35.705
So did President Yu Jin-myeong.

00:56:36.873 --> 00:56:40.960
The person who leaked the fabricated
investigation result to the media and

00:56:41.044 --> 00:56:43.421
is present here
as the special committee member.

00:56:44.047 --> 00:56:45.715
Noh Cheol-jae, the prosecutor back then.

00:56:48.635 --> 00:56:49.469
Witness!

00:56:50.178 --> 00:56:51.012
Do you have proof?

