I have the transaction history between

00:56:58.478 --> 00:57:01.648
him and Yang Hoon,
plus the recordings of our phone calls.

00:57:01.731 --> 00:57:05.193
If it's evidence you want,
I can give it to you right now.

00:57:08.863 --> 00:57:09.739
Mr. Noh.

00:57:10.323 --> 00:57:11.950
Take your seat.

00:57:12.033 --> 00:57:14.202
This time is for the witness.

00:57:20.583 --> 00:57:23.086
Lastly, the media
that influenced the public

00:57:23.169 --> 00:57:25.880
by reporting
the fabricated investigation result

00:57:26.548 --> 00:57:28.841
as if it's true
without checking the facts.

00:57:33.805 --> 00:57:34.806
All of them

00:57:35.682 --> 00:57:36.975
must be responsible.

00:57:40.645 --> 00:57:41.729
I understand.

00:57:42.647 --> 00:57:46.568
The Special Committee
will investigate that too.

00:57:47.277 --> 00:57:50.947
Thank you for testifying for a long time.

00:57:51.864 --> 00:57:53.866
Is there anything else you want to say?

00:57:53.950 --> 00:57:55.201
I'll give you time.

00:58:04.836 --> 00:58:06.379
My husband said

00:58:07.839 --> 00:58:10.633
to change the world,
he himself should change first.

00:58:12.010 --> 00:58:13.678
To change the world,

00:58:14.387 --> 00:58:15.972
you must change yourself first.

00:58:17.056 --> 00:58:19.642
By changing one person like that,

00:58:19.726 --> 00:58:21.060
you change the world.

00:58:22.228 --> 00:58:24.147
By saving one person like that,

00:58:24.230 --> 00:58:25.773
you save the world.

00:58:26.399 --> 00:58:27.567
Because

00:58:27.650 --> 00:58:29.527
each and every person

00:58:31.613 --> 00:58:33.072
is the world.

00:58:34.073 --> 00:58:37.327
Changing and saving the world.

00:58:39.329 --> 00:58:42.165
He didn't do politics
with such grandiose hope.

00:58:43.458 --> 00:58:45.293
My husband did politics

00:58:47.629 --> 00:58:50.256
because he was afraid that the world

00:58:50.340 --> 00:58:52.175
would change him.

00:58:54.344 --> 00:58:56.888
He was afraid he'd turn a blind eye
to the injured,

00:58:58.598 --> 00:59:01.851
that he'd turn his back on the coworker
who's fighting alone,

00:59:02.894 --> 00:59:05.396
and that he'd use his family and daughter

00:59:05.480 --> 00:59:08.191
as excuses to sacrifice someone

00:59:08.274 --> 00:59:10.401
and become happy on his own.

00:59:31.422 --> 00:59:32.799
I knew from the beginning

00:59:32.882 --> 00:59:35.551
that he didn't give up on anyone,
not a single person.

00:59:37.011 --> 00:59:38.137
That's why

00:59:39.639 --> 00:59:41.057
I loved him.

00:59:43.601 --> 00:59:44.852
My father

00:59:44.936 --> 00:59:47.855
sacrificed my mom
to become an assemblyman.

00:59:48.481 --> 00:59:51.567
My husband wouldn't let
anyone sacrifice themselves,

00:59:51.651 --> 00:59:55.196
even if that meant
he'd become the president.

00:59:57.031 --> 00:59:58.658
That's why

00:59:59.450 --> 01:00:00.868
I married him.

